{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"660","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"無薪假勞工薪資補助周五上路 最多月領1.1萬最長6個月","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>2020-03-25 10:10 </span><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>聯合報<span lang='EN-US'>/</span>記者葉冠妤<span lang='EN-US'>/</span>台北即時報導</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>&nbsp;<img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E7%84%A1%E8%96%AA%E5%81%87%E8%A3%9C%E5%8A%A9.JPG' style='width: 800px; height: 597px;' /></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>勞動部長許銘春今到立院衛環委員會進行業務報告。記者葉冠妤／攝影</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>受新冠肺炎疫情影響，不少受衝擊的產業實施休息減班（俗稱無薪假），勞動部將於周五推出「安心就業計畫」，補償無薪假勞工投保薪資差額的<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>成，假設勞工投保薪資最高級距為<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>萬<span lang='EN-US'>5000</span>元計算，等於最多可領到<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>萬<span lang='EN-US'>1000</span>元補貼，最長可領<span lang='EN-US'>6</span>個月。周五公告後即可申請。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>許銘春今到立院衛環委員會進行業務報告，她指出，截至昨天統計，減班休息企業有<span lang='EN-US'>164</span>家、<span lang='EN-US'>4808</span>名勞工。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>針對因應減班休息勞工推出的「安心就業計畫」，許銘春說已送進行政院，預計周五公告，公告當天勞工就可申請。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>假設勞工勞保投保最高級距<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>萬<span lang='EN-US'>5800</span>元，扣除能領到的<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>萬<span lang='EN-US'>3800</span>元基本工資，薪資差額為<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>萬<span lang='EN-US'>2000</span>元，等於可領到<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>成、<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>萬<span lang='EN-US'>1000</span>元的補貼，目前可領<span lang='EN-US'>6</span>個月。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>適用對象除一般全職勞工，包括庇護工場員工、與雇主約定固定上班天數、工時的打工族，都符合申請補貼資格。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>此外，針對非典型勞動勞工的因應措施，許銘春說，周一已初步討論，近期就會定案。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源：</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>https://udn.com/news/story/120974/4441613?from=udn-catebreaknews_ch2</span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-03-26","clk_count":"138"}},"__N_SSG":true}